{"tid":1458370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對家極怕爆眼呢單野，係超級核彈級！文宣不能停！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:28:18.000Z","uid":129387,"like":107,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"52f562a332f68b94b5b9842a334b9f87a2c7d8f1","tid":1458370,"uid":129387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"先唔講今日咩散水分化。<br />\n<br />\n我今日見到藍絲瘋狂極速廣傳假新聞，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁耐以黎未見過對家做假新聞咁快，咁齊心、咁多角度。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n612 未見過，721 未見過，唯獨是呢一單。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完全係有組織有大台有人指使要全力洗白。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">原因只得一個，呢單野既威力係核彈級別！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">平民被瞄頭用槍射，係戰爭罪行，係謀殺！！</span></span>佢地急於洗白，証明佢地真係好驚呢件事發酵！！<br />\n<br />\n我跪求各位手足，在你廣傳今日d謠言、fact check既時候，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用十倍努力去將焦點擺o係721警黑 同埋尋日女first aid被爆眼！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論做咩行動，和理非又好，勇武又好，散水又好，包圍又好，都要記住：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">毋忘721<br />\n黑警還眼<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPyOjLo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPyOjLo.jpg&h=8ef9ae2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92c465a00743cbc5f6953372e9c8f3033c6741ee","tid":1458370,"uid":25607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"2435010c1fe02862f57028a39746c022209591b2","tid":1458370,"uid":263413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1296ea5d686129d3d7f2141d3f1f7a0fce8bcf88","tid":1458370,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:56:48.000Z","